response.overview: This is about Tara a 22 year old girl who works in a music store as a part time job and she's secretly dealing with her body insecurities and zero friend circle...until she meets Ved,who is her 10th classmate and a documentary filmmaker..They'll travel together from the day they met again and tara falls in love with ved at certain point.So what happens to them at last ? Does tara overcame her insecurities or not ?..we're the remaining part of the story
response.title: DUNIYAA
